Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Gina 要给警监签名的那份文件在你这里吗\N{\fs38}Hey, Gina, you got that file I needed Captain Holt to sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\fs38}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊\N{\fs38}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gina已经两个小时没有把视线从手机上移开了\N{\fs38}Gina hasn't taken her eyes off her phone in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个让她抬头的人赢得头奖\N{\fs38}First person to make her look up wins the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入\N{\fs38}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个能让人更有礼貌的赌约 一箭双雕\N{\fs38}A bet which improves someone's manners? Double score.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 各位 这把我肯定赢\N{\fs38}Sorry, guys. I got this in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我们滚床单的时候\N{\fs38}I used to have to distract her from her phone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都要和她手机争夺她的注意力\N{\fs38}all the time when we were smooshin' booties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 恶  - 没错\N{\fs38}- Ugh. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 妹子\N{\fs38}Hey, girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会再聊\N{\fs38}Catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大早上的舞蹈派对\N{\fs38}Mid-morning dance party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她竟然比平时跳的还好\N{\fs38}She's dancing even better than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 你听说了吗 小布什死了\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, did you hear that George W. Bush died?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁\N{\fs38}Who dat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\N{\fs38}Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gina可能再也不会抬头看现实生活中的人了\N{\fs38}Gina may never look at another real human being again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是不可战胜的\N{\fs38}She's unbeatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那可不一定喔\N{\fs38}Oh, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terrence Jeffords 你开玩笑呢吧\N{\fs38}Terrence Jeffords, are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚把感情状态改成了"一言难尽"\N{\fs38}Changed my relationship status to "It's complicated."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,付账吧 各位\N{\fs38}Pony up, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔噢\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老婆的电话\N{\fs38}It's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 宝贝\N{\fs38}Hey, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不不 我按错了\N{\fs38}No! No, no, no. It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手滑了然后就 我要回家一趟\N{\fs38}My thumb slipped and... I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fs38}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是我人生中最棒的一天\N{\fs38}today is the greatest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们猜谁被谋杀了\N{\fs38}Guess who just got murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是Carl Mather\N{\fs38}That's right... it's Carl Mather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么只有我在倒吸一口凉气\N{\fs38}What? I'm the only one gasping?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 这是Carl Mather啊 蹲了25年的号子\N{\fs38}Guys, Carl Mather? Did 25 years in Attica...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好意思\N{\fs38}Sor... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我吸气的时候朝我指一下就好\N{\fs38}Just point at me when you want me to gasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\fs38}Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mather是富尔顿街四人帮成员之一\N{\fs38}Mather is part of the Fulton Street Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从一个装甲车检修处盗窃了两千一百万美金\N{\fs38}They stole $21 million from an armored car depot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦探员抓到了他们 但一直没能把钱找回来\N{\fs38}Feds caught them but they never found the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 直到现在  - 你找回那两千一百万了吗\N{\fs38}- Until now. - You found $21 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒没有 还没呢\N{\fs38}Oh, God no. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我刚说的话是有点容易让人误解\N{\fs38}I can see how that would be confusing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 但我会找到的\N{\fs38}I'm sorry. But I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的六个月里\N{\fs38}Over the past six months,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这四个人都刑满释放了\N{\fs38}all four of these guys have been released,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在其中一人死了\N{\fs38}and now one of them shows up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有人惦记上那笔钱了\N{\fs38}Someone's after that money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜杀人来得到它\N{\fs38}and they're willing to kill for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你话说的太早了吧\N{\fs38}You're getting ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不知道Mather的死亡\N{\fs38}You don't know that Mather's death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定跟那笔钱有关系\N{\fs38}is connected to the money yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把这个案子变得比原本更复杂\N{\fs38}Don't turn this into something bigger than it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是在Madeline Wuntch一直看着我们的时候\N{\fs38}not with Madeline Wuntch watching us at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶 这是什么时候挂上去的\N{\fs38}Ew. When'd they put that in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在Wuntch升职之后\N{\fs38}Right after Wuntch got promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把画像挂在高处 这样她就能\N{\fs38}She had it installed at that height so she'd,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引用她的原话来说就是"一直俯视着我"\N{\fs38}I quote, "Always be looking down at me," Unquote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个案子当成普通案子来办\N{\fs38}Treat this like a regular case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 无意冒犯 但这是个传奇的案子\N{\fs38}Sir, with all due respect, this is an epic case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我成为警察的原因\N{\fs38}It's the reason I became a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追查谋杀犯\N{\fs38}I mean, hunting down a murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找回被盗的百万现金\N{\fs38}recovering millions in stolen money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用牙叼着刀 从直升灰机上抓着绳子滑下来\N{\fs38}rappelling out of a chopper with a knife between my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要叼着刀 从直升飞机上跳下来\N{\fs38}Why would you jump out of a helicopter with a knife in your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是直升灰机 而我之所以会叼着刀\N{\fs38}It's called a chopper, and the knife is in my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我的双手正扛着一把机关枪\N{\fs38}because both of my hands are holding giant machine guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,论如何正确地下飞机\N{\fs38}And that's how it's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 提醒一下 \N{\fs38}Okay, reminder,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天布鲁克林公园重点(磁铁)中学要来我们这里参观\N{\fs38}tomorrow we are hosting a field trip for the Brooklyn Park Magnet School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 警长 我不能呆在磁铁旁边\N{\fs38}Sorry, Sarge, I can't be around magnets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴着心脏起搏器呢\N{\fs38}Pacemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不纠正你了\N{\fs38}I'm actually not gonna correct you on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 这次一定不能出差错\N{\fs38}Guys, I really need this to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿在这间学校的幼儿园的等候名单上\N{\fs38}My girls are on the wait list for their preschool
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且双胞胎要进去简直难度加倍\N{\fs38}and it's twice as tough to get in with twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不让一个人进去读\N{\fs38}Why don't you just get one of them in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让她们两个每天轮流上学\N{\fs38}and then let them take turns going to school every other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Diaz 这方法太疯狂了\N{\fs38}Diaz, that's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问了我老婆 她说不行\N{\fs38}I asked my wife and she said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次参观一定得顺利\N{\fs38}This field trip has to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个能让我给校长留下深刻印象的机会\N{\fs38}This is my chance to impress the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长 你走运了\N{\fs38}Sarge, you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前上的就是重点中学 而且我还被评为\N{\fs38}I went to a magnet school where I was voted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"最有可能跟学校管理人员成为朋友的人"\N{\fs38}"Most likely to befriend a school administrator."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 Amy\N{\fs38}Oh, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟青春期前的小孩最玩的来了\N{\fs38}Preteens are my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟他们有共同语言\N{\fs38}I speak their language.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定会玩的很开心的\N{\fs38}They are gonna have an amazing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 太好了\N{\fs38}Thanks, guys. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意 我可以给他们看一些\N{\fs38}If you want, I can show them some of the cool stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据箱里面很有意思的东西\N{\fs38}we have in the evidence locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很确定里面有一袋人手\N{\fs38}I'm pretty sure there's a bag of hands in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不行不行\N{\fs38}Whoa! No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要营造一个儿童适宜的环境\N{\fs38}We got to make this place kid-friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把罪案现场的照片到处放\N{\fs38}No crime scene photos lying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张不是罪案现场\N{\fs38}That's not a crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我准备框起来送我老婆的闺房密照\N{\fs38}That's a boudoir photo I'm having framed for my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面具下的人就是在下\N{\fs38}That's me underneath the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fs38}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 我们要采访一下邻居\N{\fs38}Next, let's get statements from the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你好啊警监\N{\fs38}Ah, hello, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案情新发展 \N{\fs38}Quick update.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个富尔顿街四人帮成员今天早上被谋杀了\N{\fs38}Another one of the Fulton Street Four was murdered here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 我很惊讶你没有不合时宜地庆祝这个消息\N{\fs38}Huh, I'm surprised you're not celebrating inappropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个罪案现场 我是个有职业操守的警察\N{\fs38}This is a crime scene and I'm a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我来之前庆祝了吧\N{\fs38}You did it before I showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是那样\N{\fs38}Yeah, that is exactly correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个成员在两日之内被谋杀\N{\fs38}So two of these guys murdered in the past two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定跟被盗的巨款有关\N{\fs38}It has to be tied to the missing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认我是对的吧\N{\fs38}Admit I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些情况确实指示出某种联系\N{\fs38}Circumstances do suggest a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认的直白一点\N{\fs38}Admit it with more gusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你是对的  - 耶 你录下来了吗 Boyle\N{\fs38}- You were right. - Yes! Did you get it, Boyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 手机相机开的是自拍模式\N{\fs38}Oh, the camera was in selfie mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到了我深深为你骄傲的样子\N{\fs38}but I look super proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏消息是 因为这案子变大了\N{\fs38}Unfortunately, because this case has turned out to be important,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人渣(臭鼬)Madeline Wuntch把她的后腿伸向了它\N{\fs38}that she-skunk Madeline Wuntch has her hindquarters pointed right at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要我们去她办公室一趟\N{\fs38}She wants to see us in her office,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定会把这案子给重案组\N{\fs38}no doubt to give the case to Major Crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 不能让这种事发生\N{\fs38}No, no, no. We can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 我们得做点什么\N{\fs38}Sir, we have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我去色诱她\N{\fs38}Fine. I'll seduce her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去穿上我的单车短裤\N{\fs38}I'll just put on my bike shorts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她欣赏我雄伟的下半身\N{\fs38}and give her a glimpse of the quad cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是这个意思\N{\fs38}No. No. That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是我们要对抗她\N{\fs38}I meant we have to fight her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能跟她对抗 她是魔鬼\N{\fs38}We're not gonna fight her. She's the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能与魔鬼共舞 因为你会被地狱之火烧伤的\N{\fs38}And you don't dance with the devil, because you get burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 关于Madeline\N{\fs38}Also, because in Madeline's case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跳舞没有节奏感 手就像老鼠的爪子一样\N{\fs38}she has no rhythm and her hands are like little rat claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她要这个案子 那就给她\N{\fs38}If she wants the case, it's hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下 你把这个谋杀案现场\N{\fs38}For the record, you're turning this murder scene
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了真的无趣之地\N{\fs38}into a real bummer-scape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的有力反击拍下来了吧\N{\fs38}Tell me you got that zinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 相机又是自拍模式\N{\fs38}Oh, the camera was in selfie mode again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我刚笑得真是灿烂啊\N{\fs38}but I was really laughing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 孩子们 这就是我们警探小分队破案的地方\N{\fs38}Okay, kids, this is where my detective squad solves crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哇  - 这是我的办公桌\N{\fs38}- Wow. - This is my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以通过这个我3岁女儿们自己拼的\N{\fs38}You can tell by the framed 200-piece puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200片的拼图辨认出来\N{\fs38}my three-year-olds put together on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们很早慧嘛 Jeffords警长\N{\fs38}That's very advanced, Sergeant Jeffords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我也不知道什么成就能让学校招生办留下深刻印象啦\N{\fs38}Is it? I wouldn't know what milestones are impressive to a school admissions officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们能用英文和中文从1数到20\N{\fs38}They can count to 20 in English and Mandarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我是Santiago警探 重点中学女校友(拉丁语)\N{\fs38}Hi. Detective Santiago, magnet school alumna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很欣赏你对女校友这个词的正确用法\N{\fs38}Well, I appreciate that you used the proper declension of alumnus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说 拉丁语是一门已经死亡的语言\N{\fs38}Well, some say Latin is a dead language,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得它只是在打一个很长的盹儿\N{\fs38}but I say it's just taking a long nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧 你们两个明显是大姐大\N{\fs38}Okay, you two are obviously the alphas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我猜猜\N{\fs38}Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟那个金发男孩约会 而你喜欢那个菲律宾丁日\N{\fs38}You're dating the blond kid and you like Filipino Bieber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你担心他还喜欢着那个编侧麻花辫 背劣质包的姑娘\N{\fs38}but you're worried he's still into little Miss Side Braid Janky Purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fs38}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都知道\N{\fs38}I know so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我叫Gina\N{\fs38}Hi, I'm Gina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Raymond\N{\fs38}Hello, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我的新办公室怎么样 在20楼哦\N{\fs38}How do you like my new office? 20th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我从来没有在这么高的地方见过你\N{\fs38}Yes, I never thought I'd see you this high
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你骑着扫把的时候\N{\fs38}without a broom under you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,示好结束 坐吧\N{\fs38}Enough niceties. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 但我站着就好了\N{\fs38}Thanks, but I'm actually fine standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以这样酷酷站一整天噢\N{\fs38}I could stay in these bad boys all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两名富尔顿街四人帮成员被谋杀了\N{\fs38}So two members of the Fulton Street Four
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来是个大案子啊\N{\fs38}have been murdered... sounds like a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 正好相反\N{\fs38}No, it's actually the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是个没啥大的情况\N{\fs38}Pretty much an NBT sitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啥大不了\N{\fs38}No big thang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是"没什么大不了" 但这案子是挺大不了的\N{\fs38}The word is "Thing," And the thing is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为有人惦记上失窃的两千一百万了\N{\fs38}We believe someone is after the missing $21 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果破了这起谋杀案 我们就能找回这笔钱\N{\fs38}and solving this murder could lead us to the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但这笔钱已经差不多25岁了\N{\fs38}Sure, but that money's, like, 25 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能都不好使了呢\N{\fs38}It's probably not even good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 抽筋了\N{\fs38}Sorry. Cramped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个很重要的案子 Raymond\N{\fs38}This is a very important case, Raymond,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我 对于纽约来说都是的\N{\fs38}to me, and to the city of New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不确定九九片区有处理这种大案的资源\N{\fs38}I'm not sure the Nine-Nine has the resources to deal with something of this magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂规定\N{\fs38}I understand the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个备受瞩目的案子\N{\fs38}This is a high-profile case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做你该做的吧\N{\fs38}Do what you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是\N{\fs38}What I was going to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们没有那些资源\N{\fs38}since you don't have the resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你们提供你们需要的东西\N{\fs38}I'll give you anything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案子是你们的 我会全力支持\N{\fs38}The case is yours. You have my full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想表达得更激动的 像这样"神马"\N{\fs38}He meant that more excited. Like, "What!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 富尔顿街四人帮死了两个\N{\fs38}Okay, two of the Fulton Street Four are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的直觉 其中一个在杀他的"同渣"\N{\fs38}My hunch... one of them is killing off his co-scums
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他"渣己"就能独吞赃款了\N{\fs38}so he can keep the money for his scum-self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从Reggie Bludsoe入手\N{\fs38}We'll start with Reggie Bludsoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在假释官那里留了布鲁克林的地址\N{\fs38}He listed a Brooklyn address with his parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定能搞定这人渣的\N{\fs38}We're gonna nail this son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非他无辜\N{\fs38}Unless he's innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样我们就救下这人渣\N{\fs38}then we're gonna have the son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 这案子绝对会很棒的\N{\fs38}Either way, this case is gonna be awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peralta 我要和你一起调查这案子\N{\fs38}Peralta, I'm putting myself on this investigation with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么 为什么  - Wuntch在盘算着什么\N{\fs38}- What? Why? - Wuntch is up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她让我们留着这案子只有一个原因\N{\fs38}There's only one reason why she would let us keep this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看了我一眼 然后说道\N{\fs38}She took one look at me and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我就想这小伙去开直升灰机"\N{\fs38}"That's the guy I want flying my chopper."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道怎么开直升灰机吗\N{\fs38}You know how to fly a chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么难的\N{\fs38}How hard could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个飞上天的大风扇吗\N{\fs38}It's just a big fan that goes in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她让我们留着这案子是因为她希望我们失败\N{\fs38}She let us keep this case because she wants us to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一起去调查 \N{\fs38}I'm coming along
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就不会浪费时间和资源 \N{\fs38}so that you don't waste time and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这次调查弄成另一部Ron McClan的电影\N{\fs38}turning this investigation into another Ron McClane movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs39}John McClane 电影<虎胆龙威>的主角 布鲁斯·威利斯出演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是John McClane\N{\fs38}Oh, you know it's John McClane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下定决心 就这样吧\N{\fs38}I've made my decision. End of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fs38}All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你得自己开车\N{\fs38}But you're gonna have to take your own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把毒贩的兰博基尼从扣押处提出来了\N{\fs38}I signed out that drug dealer's Lamborghini from the impound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那车只有两个座位\N{\fs38}It only has two seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到你那个申请了\N{\fs38}I saw that you had made that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我换成合适的小轿车了\N{\fs38}I changed it to a sensible sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是遮阳蓬必须打开\N{\fs38}Okay, but the sunroof stays open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这车没有遮阳蓬\N{\fs38}There is no sunroof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当警察干什么来了\N{\fs38}Why did you even become a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 孩子们\N{\fs38}Oh, great job, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别破太多案子 搞得我失业了\N{\fs38}Don't solve too many crimes and put me out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terry还得付房租呢\N{\fs38}Terry's got to pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Susman老师想和我单独谈谈\N{\fs38}Dr. Susman wants a private chat with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你让她感觉良好 Santiago\N{\fs38}Thanks for warming her up, Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师们可不会无缘无故给八年级的Amy教师休息室的钥匙\N{\fs38}They didn't give eighth grade Amy the key to the teacher's lounge just for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给他们冰箱补货 在他们走后打扫清洁\N{\fs38}I stocked their fridge and cleaned up after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你能接管这些孩子一会儿吗\N{\fs38}Great. So can you take over with the kids for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经完成这个活动了\N{\fs38}They're done with this activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 我和孩子处得可好了\N{\fs38}Of course. I am amazing with kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和孩子完全处不来\N{\fs38}I am terrible with kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经三年没听饶舌音乐了\N{\fs38}I haven't listened to rap music in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么交谈 得你来才行\N{\fs38}I don't know the lingo. You have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 McKenzie在厕所里恐慌症犯了\N{\fs38}I can't... McKenzie is in the bathroom right now freaking out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Kelsey S和Hayes亲热了\N{\fs38}because Kelsey S. Made out with Hayes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管她知道Brianna喜欢他\N{\fs38}even though she knows Brianna's into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你想让春季舞会成撕逼大会\N{\fs38}So unless you want the spring dance to be a total drama fest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我必须得在这儿陪她\N{\fs38}I have to be there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没搞懂\N{\fs38}I don't....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 你应该给他们看看死人的照片\N{\fs38}Honestly, you should show them a picture of a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 Rosa Terry说了要适合孩子的\N{\fs38}No! Rosa, Terry said to keep it kid-friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我就给他们看我那个年纪的时候喜欢的东西\N{\fs38}Okay, I'll just show them the stuff that I was into when I was their age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我完成了  - 我们现在干什么\N{\fs38}- I'm done. - What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 接下来呢  - 你们好啊 小朋友\N{\fs38}- What's next? - Hello, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们谁想看按照人口和时间为变量的\N{\fs38}Who here would like to see a presentation about crime statistics
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪统计的报告啊\N{\fs38}as a function of demographics and time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想看死人的照片\N{\fs38}Who wants to see a picture of a dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs38}Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bludsoe就住在这走廊尽头\N{\fs38}Bludsoe lives at the end of his hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我更喜欢废弃灯塔或者破旧的仓库 \N{\fs38}Hmm... I would have preferred an abandoned lighthouse or a dilapidated barn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可以在回忆录里稍作修饰\N{\fs38}but I can embellish in my memoirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 我等不及看那本书了\N{\fs38}Oh, I can't wait to read that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备取什么名字\N{\fs38}What are you gonna call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"快'杰'全我的一天 "\N{\fs38}"Go Ahead, Jake My Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你的更好\N{\fs38}No, yours is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"案件完结 杰克开始"\N{\fs38}"Case Closed, Jake Open."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 喔  - 我懂\N{\fs38}- Wow. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了你的更好嘛\N{\fs38}I said yours was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 我们开始吧\N{\fs38}Whatever. Let's just do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警局 开门\N{\fs38}NYPD. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 快看\N{\fs38}Hey, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打包完的行李箱\N{\fs38}Half-packed suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来Bludsoe准备出游\N{\fs38}Looks like Bludsoe was planning a trip
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到被某人打扰了\N{\fs38}until he got interrupted by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 或者某事  - 比如\N{\fs38}- Or something. - Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我只是觉得这样会增加悬念\N{\fs38}I don't know... I just thought it would help the intrigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是\N{\fs38}It did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再闲扯了\N{\fs38}That's enough chitchat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样嘛 得有多少人被杀\N{\fs38}Come on, how many people have to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才能开始享乐啊 \N{\fs38}before you start having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们的工作是阻止人被杀吧\N{\fs38}You do know it's our job to stop the killing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs38}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像闻到了死人的气味\N{\fs38}I think I smell a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我错了\N{\fs38}Nope. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 别关\N{\fs38}Wait! Don't close that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 指纹\N{\fs38}Look. Handprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是面假墙\N{\fs38}That's a fake wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约警局\N{\fs38}Nypd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放到头上出来\N{\fs38}Come out with your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 别开枪\N{\fs38}Don't shoot! Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想杀我\N{\fs38}He's trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想噢 非要说的话\N{\fs38}So I guess, if I had to sum them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cagney的智商更高一点\N{\fs38}Cagney is the intellectual one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而Lacey更像是传统的那种天才\N{\fs38}whereas Lacey is more of your traditional prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 你女儿们听起来都很棒啊\N{\fs38}Well, your daughters sound great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再看看她们的申请材料的\N{\fs38}You know, I'm gonna look over their applications again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用劳烦了\N{\fs38}Oh, no, that's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓氏是Jeffords 双写f\N{\fs38}It's Jeffords with two Fs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正重要的是你的学生今天有一次美好的经历\N{\fs38}But what really matters is that your students have an amazing experience here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 Rosa 警长来了\N{\fs38}Look, Rosa. Sarge is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们 快离开这个房间\N{\fs38}Children, get out of this room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs38}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们搞什么鬼\N{\fs38}What the hell, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们才十二岁\N{\fs38}They're 12 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那个年纪愿意付出一切去看一袋人手\N{\fs38}I would've killed to have seen a bag of hands at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉 我本想做自己 但是他们不喜欢\N{\fs38}I'm so sorry... I tired to be myself and they hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿了  - 拯救这一天啊\N{\fs38}- Where were you? - Saving the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayes已经不算事儿了\N{\fs38}Hayes is out of the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,McKenzie和Kelsey S.纠纷已经解决\N{\fs38}The McKenzie/Kelsey S. Beef is squashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Brianna会和Aidan一起去舞会\N{\fs38}and Brianna's going to the dance with Aidan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他也更配的上她\N{\fs38}who's a much better match for her anyway, BT-dubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说有什么用\N{\fs38}How does any of that help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Susman老师  - 再见 Jeffords警长\N{\fs38}- Dr. Susman... - Good-bye, Sergeant Jeffords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这次的经历对于孩子们来说真是够了\N{\fs38}I think this experience has been more than enough for the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参观就这样结束吧\N{\fs38}We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正从咖啡店走回家\N{\fs38}I was walking home from the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那里谈工作\N{\fs38}I have a job bussing tables there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 Mikey D就把一把枪抵在我背上\N{\fs38}Anyway, the next thing I know, Mikey D has a gun in my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Michael D'Angelo 富尔顿四人帮的另一个成员\N{\fs38}Michael D'Angelo, the other member of the Fulton Street Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不管你们信不信 \N{\fs38}Yes, believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很熟悉我们负责的这起备受瞩目的谋杀案中\N{\fs38}I familiarized myself with the names of all two suspects
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有两位嫌疑人的名字\N{\fs38}in this high-profile homicide we're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反抗了 但是他拿了我的钥匙\N{\fs38}I fought him off, but he got my key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钥匙用来干什么的\N{\fs38}What's the key for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们四人一人一把\N{\fs38}Each of us had one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得要集齐四把才能开保险柜\N{\fs38}and you needed all four to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保险柜里有什么\N{\fs38}And what's in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两千一百万美金\N{\fs38}The $21 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜 头彩\N{\fs38}Bing... pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我本来想说"猜中了"\N{\fs38}Nope... I was gonna say bingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是突然觉得"中头彩"更好\N{\fs38}but then I was like, "Jackpot's better,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是来不及改口 已经说了一半了\N{\fs38}but then it was too late; I was halfway through the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜头彩也行 也很顺口\N{\fs38}Bingpot works. It's taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很顺口\N{\fs38}It's taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 D'Angelo在州北部有房产\N{\fs38}Captain, D'Angelo has a place upstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地治安官说现在就有辆车停在车道上\N{\fs38}The local sheriff says there's a car in the driveway right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定在那儿\N{\fs38}He must be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 他们得自己突击了 不能等我们\N{\fs38}Okay, they're gonna have to raid the place without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到达得花两个小时\N{\fs38}It'll take us two hours to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我们可以坐\N{\fs38}Or we could take...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会坐直升飞机\N{\fs38}We are not taking a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是想说直升灰机\N{\fs38}You know I was gonna say chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peralta 我知道你在享乐\N{\fs38}Look, Peralta, I know you're having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果一旦出了差错 出动直升飞机这种浪费经费的行为\N{\fs38}but a helicopter is exactly the kind of wasteful expenditure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被Wuntch用来打击我\N{\fs38}that Wuntch will use to bury me if something goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧 长官  - 或许\N{\fs38}- Okay, sir... - Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没用的话 她也会拿来攻击我\N{\fs38}It's the kind of thing she'll crucify me for not getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你本可以使用直升灰机的 Raymond"\N{\fs38}"You could've had a chopper, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"为什么不充分利用资源呢"\N{\fs38}"Why didn't you take advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 我现在脑子有点乱\N{\fs38}Just a minute... my cauldron's boiling over."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上她说的是\N{\fs38}Yeah, but what she actually said was,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"直升机是你的了 Peralta"\N{\fs38}"Chopper's yours, Peralta."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你学得更像\N{\fs38}Your impression was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么\N{\fs38}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也许打电话给我了 我也许和她汇报了情况\N{\fs38}She may have called me and I may have briefed her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她也许同意了使用直升灰机\N{\fs38}and she may have said yes to the chopper
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为直升灰机正在途中\N{\fs38}because it's definitely on its way right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间位置是我的\N{\fs38}I call middle seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\N{\fs38}Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太棒了\N{\fs38}This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们说清楚 从现在开始\N{\fs38}Okay, just so we're clear, from this point forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的代号是死亡剑客\N{\fs38}my call sign will be Death Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是Rum Tum Tugger\N{\fs38}And I'll be Rum Tum Tugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 Boyle 不能用音乐剧<猫>里的角色名\N{\fs38}No, Boyle. No characters from Cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想 想个吓人的名字\N{\fs38}Dig deep. Think of something scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿道夫·希特勒\N{\fs38}Adolf Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就叫 响尾蛇\N{\fs38}You will be... Sidewinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是希特勒更吓人\N{\fs38}All right, but I'm more scared of Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢 警监 你的代号是什么\N{\fs38}How about you, Captain? What's your call sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就叫Raymond Holt警监\N{\fs38}I will be Captain Raymond Holt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你不会配合\N{\fs38}Uh-huh, I knew you wouldn't play ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你的代号是扫兴鬼\N{\fs38}And that is why your call sign is Wet Blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响尾蛇 我是死亡剑客\N{\fs38}Sidewinder, this is Death Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到了吗 响尾蛇 完毕\N{\fs38}Do you copy, Sidewinder? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是响尾蛇 死亡剑客\N{\fs38}This is Sidewinder, Death Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消息已收到 完毕\N{\fs38}I read you loud and clear. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有发现扫兴鬼的位置吗 响尾蛇\N{\fs38}Do you have a 20 on Wet Blanket, Sidewinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\fs38}Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我发现了  - 完毕\N{\fs38}- I do have a visual... - Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 警监 \N{\fs38}All right, look, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wuntch说了 为了解决这案子 \N{\fs38}Wuntch said that we could have anything we needed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要什么都行\N{\fs38}to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是为什么呢\N{\fs38}Yes, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了抓住一个偷了两千一百万的杀人犯\N{\fs38}To catch a murder who stole $21 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是为了让我们的失败显得更加引人注目\N{\fs38}No, it's so that when we do fail, it'll be that much more spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们不抓到D'Angelo 我的事业就完了\N{\fs38}If we don't get D'Angelo, my career is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:14:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我们抓到了他 你的事业就会真正地腾飞\N{\fs38}But if we do catch him, your career will really take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升灰机双关语\N{\fs38}Chopper pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Susman博士 我真的非常非常抱歉\N{\fs38}Dr. Susman, I am so, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托不要因为这个针对我的女儿们\N{\fs38}Please don't hold this against my daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会那样做\N{\fs38}I would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预科学校招生是基于我们对家长的看法\N{\fs38}Preschool admissions are based on what we think of the parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不\N{\fs38}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Susman博士\N{\fs38}Dr. Susman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nancy 如果我可以这样称呼你的话\N{\fs38}Nancy, if I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你不可以  - 好的\N{\fs38}- You may not. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我们的方法可能有点非传统\N{\fs38}Look, our methods may have been a little unorthodox,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还有一点\N{\fs38}and perhaps a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过度形象并且令人作呕\N{\fs38}Graphic and disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想说小恶心的\N{\fs38}I was gonna go with yucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这些孩子今天玩得很开心\N{\fs38}But these kids had fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且学到了很多\N{\fs38}And they learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tricia 什么是鲁米诺\N{\fs38}Tricia, what's Luminol?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它用于在犯罪现场寻找血迹\N{\fs38}It's used to look for blood in a crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使罪犯试图清理血迹\N{\fs38}Even if a criminal tried to clean it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血液中的铁使得化学物质发光\N{\fs38}the iron in blood makes the chemical glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 Bobby 什么叫眼球摘除术\N{\fs38}And, Bobby, what's enucleation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有人把你的眼珠子弹出来\N{\fs38}It's when someone pops your eyeball out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时应该举个不那么恶心的例子\N{\fs38}Probably should've used a less gross example.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是\N{\fs38}The point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这样的教育经历让我热爱我的重点学校\N{\fs38}this is exactly the kind of educational experience i loved about my magnet school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点还有待讨论\N{\fs38}Well, there's something to be said for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 更重要的是 \N{\fs38}Also, and more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让McKenzie和Brianna不再讨厌Kelsey S了\N{\fs38}I got McKenzie and Brianna to stop hating on Kelsey S.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们是最好的朋友了 不用谢\N{\fs38}And now they're best friends... you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 那其实挺厉害的\N{\fs38}Wow, that's actually impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 Susman博士\N{\fs38}So, Dr. Susman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们为这次参观之旅正名\N{\fs38}let's just call this field trip what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次巨大的成功\N{\fs38}a huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它挺 有趣的\N{\fs38}It was... interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了一个妓女耶\N{\fs38}I saw a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别帮倒忙了 小子\N{\fs38}Not helping, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D'Angelo的住处就在那些树后面\N{\fs38}D'Angelo's place is just beyond those trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有人进出\N{\fs38}No one's gone in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我们及时赶到\N{\fs38}Good thing we got here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐直升灰机过来的\N{\fs38}Flew in on a chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bell412还是A119Koala\N{\fs38}Bell 412 or the A119 Koala?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是机密\N{\fs38}It's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 是一架350B2\N{\fs38}Actually, it was the 350B2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错\N{\fs38}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 别让他说"不错"\N{\fs38}No, don't give him the "Nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有看到任何屋内的动静\N{\fs38}We haven't seen any movement in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谷仓里有灯光\N{\fs38}but there are lights on in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有个谷仓\N{\fs38}There's a barn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么对谷仓这么痴迷\N{\fs38}What is your fascination with barns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是所有屌炸天的对决发生的地方\N{\fs38}It's where all the awesome stand-offs happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生锈的农场用具 光线从弹孔透入\N{\fs38}rusty farm equipment, light shining through bullet holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你打赌至少会有一只鸽子慢动作起飞\N{\fs38}I'll bet you at least one dove takes flight in slo-mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你赌 因为那是不可能的\N{\fs38}I will take that bet, because that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后门有一支小分队\N{\fs38}We've got a team on the back entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一队人在盯着房子 那座小山上还有个狙击手\N{\fs38}a team watching the house, and a marksman on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 告诉你的人如果他们先找到钱\N{\fs38}Okay, tell your men if they find the money first,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在耳边洗一遍然后说\N{\fs38}that I get to riffle it next to my ear and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"都在这儿了"\N{\fs38}"It's all here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 已经告诉他们了 Jake  - 爱你 兄弟\N{\fs38}- Already told them, Jake. - Love you, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 子弹上膛伙计们\N{\fs38}All right, let's lock and load.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞得比我想象的快 但还是很酷\N{\fs38}Moved faster than I was expecting, but still cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到他\N{\fs38}I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 他在这儿呢\N{\fs38}Oh, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到\N{\fs38}I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在呢 他死了\N{\fs38}He is. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 尸体就在这里\N{\fs38}- What? - The body is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 Bludsoe耍了我们\N{\fs38}Damn it! Bludsoe played us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快接 快接 快接\N{\fs38}Pick up, pick up, pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈喽  - 嘿 我是Peralta\N{\fs38}- Hello? - Hey, it's Peralta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bludsoe还在拘留中吗\N{\fs38}Is Bludsoe still in custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们关着他呢 他在他的\N{\fs38}Yeah, we got him. He's in his...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟\N{\fs38}Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 先说好消息\N{\fs38}So... good news first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去会飞过美丽的日落\N{\fs38}We're gonna be flying back past a beautiful sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏消息 Bludsoe从医院逃跑了\N{\fs38}Bad news... Bludsoe escaped from the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都完蛋了\N{\fs38}and we're all screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有漂亮的日落噢\N{\fs38}But... Pretty sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 伙计 看看警监\N{\fs38}Oh, man, look at the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在缓慢地踱步\N{\fs38}He's pacing slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于他 那就像全开的愤怒大爆发\N{\fs38}For him, that's like a full-on, rage-fueled freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一更糟的就是他站着一动不动的时候\N{\fs38}The only thing worse is when he stands perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不 他完全静止了\N{\fs38}Oh, no, he's standing perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我要去跟他谈谈\N{\fs38}All right, I'm gonna go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不我不去\N{\fs38}Mm, no I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我要去 不 我才不去\N{\fs38}Yep, I am. No, I'm not gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我去 我这就去\N{\fs38}Okay, I am. I'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 小心点\N{\fs38}Okay. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你真勇敢  - 谢谢\N{\fs38}- You're so brave. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 警监\N{\fs38}Hey, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么呢\N{\fs38}What you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是Madeline Wuntch会怎么毁灭我\N{\fs38}Mostly about how Madeline Wuntch will destroy me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你想要一架直升机来演动作片\N{\fs38}because you wanted a helicopter to play action movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要直升机是因为我在追捕一个坏人\N{\fs38}I needed the helicopter because I was chasing a bad guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是个警察\N{\fs38}because I'm a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 不是只想要让这个案子变得传奇吗\N{\fs38}Really? It wasn't just to make this case epic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个案子是很传奇\N{\fs38}This case is epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是被政治蒙混了头脑看不见\N{\fs38}You're just too wrapped up in the politics to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 我们在追踪一个偷了两千一百万美金\N{\fs38}Sir, we're tracking a triple murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了三个人的罪犯\N{\fs38}who stole $21 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想到的只有Madeline Wuntch\N{\fs38}and all you can think about is Madeline Wuntch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你说得对  - 你说什么\N{\fs38}- You're right. - What's that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我来九九片区之前\N{\fs38}Before I came to the Nine-Nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在公共关系部门的一个办公桌后面慢慢腐烂\N{\fs38}I was rotting away behind a desk in the public relations department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的只是一个再次做个好警察的机会\N{\fs38}All I wanted was the chance to do good police work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚得到这个机会 我却浪费它想着那个邪恶的癞蛤蟆\N{\fs38}I just got it, and I blew it thinking about that devil toad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够政治了\N{\fs38}I'm tired of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去抓住那个混蛋Bludsoe\N{\fs38}Let's get that punk! Bludsoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是棒呆了\N{\fs38}This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我们完全不知道他在哪里\N{\fs38}Of course, we have no idea where he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我欣赏你的想法\N{\fs38}but I love where your head's at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有家人\N{\fs38}He has no family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有个女朋友\N{\fs38}Maybe there was a girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者某个咖啡店的同事\N{\fs38}or someone he worked with at the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡店 为什么一个知道自己会有两千一百万美元的人\N{\fs38}The coffee shop... why would someone who knows they have $21 million coming
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会做一份最低薪资的工作呢\N{\fs38}take a minimum wage job?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他需要进入那栋建筑\N{\fs38}Because he needed access to that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那就是钱藏着的地方\N{\fs38}Because that's where the money's hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们得尽快赶到那儿\N{\fs38}All right, we got to get there quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们应该坐直升灰机\N{\fs38}Maybe we should take the chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了直升灰机\N{\fs38}You said chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡刀锋 响尾蛇 是时候出发了\N{\fs38}Death Blade, Sidewinder, it's go time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到 扫兴鬼\N{\fs38}Roger that, Wet Blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 从今以后 叫我\N{\fs38}No, from now on, call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天鹅绒雷霆\N{\fs38}Velvet Thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Cagney和Lacey离开等候名单了\N{\fs38}Hey, Cagney and Lacey got off the wait list.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们帮我\N{\fs38}Thank you, guys, for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rosa 我本应该听你的\N{\fs38}Rosa, I should've listened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 每个人都应该听我的\N{\fs38}Yeah, everyone should listen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时 不论何事\N{\fs38}all the time about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺好玩的 孩子们其实喜欢我\N{\fs38}It was pretty fun. The kids actually liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我能回到初中\N{\fs38}I wish I could go back to middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着我现在的知识\N{\fs38}knowing what I know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定超酷的\N{\fs38}I'd be so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能重做所有的考试\N{\fs38}And I'd get to retake all the tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更新一些读书报告\N{\fs38}And update some book reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 对了 Gina Susman博士说\N{\fs38}Oh, un, Gina, Dr. Susman said
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对那些孩子产生了真正的影响\N{\fs38}you had a real impact on those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然 你刚被命名为春季舞会公主\N{\fs38}Apparently, you were just named spring Dance Princess somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼 我一直以来都跟你们说什么呢\N{\fs38}Mm-hmm, what am I always telling you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是皇族\N{\fs38}I'm royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 听着\N{\fs38}All right, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快速有力地出击\N{\fs38}We go in strong and we go in fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evans 你负责破门\N{\fs38}Evans, you're on door breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Patterson 你扔闪光弹\N{\fs38}Patterson... flashbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Boyle 别再那么深蹲了\N{\fs38}Boyle, stop squatting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我以为这样很酷\N{\fs38}Sorry, I thought it looked cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 并没有  - 数三下\N{\fs38}- It didn't. - On the count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Bludsoe\N{\fs38}It's Bludsoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 纽约警局  - 走 走 走\N{\fs38}- NYPD! - Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸朝下 趴在地上\N{\fs38}Facedown, flat on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 这里 这里\N{\fs38}Hey, over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜头彩\N{\fs38}Bingpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太酷了\N{\fs38}This rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的梦想一直是\N{\fs38}Did you know that my dream has always been to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一堆被追回的现金合照吗\N{\fs38}have my picture taken with a mountain of recovered cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以来的梦想就是给你照那张照片 Jake\N{\fs38}And it's always been my dream to take that picture of you, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 噢  - 耶\N{\fs38}- Oh. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs38}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两千一百万 Raymond\N{\fs38}$21 million, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须承认 你让我刮目相看\N{\fs38}I have to admit, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你失望了 Madeline\N{\fs38}Sorry to disappoint you, Madeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你希望我们失败\N{\fs38}I know you'd hoped we'd fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦不 我高兴得不得了\N{\fs38}Oh, no, I couldn't be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你为什么那么说\N{\fs38}Wait... Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么没有愤怒地握紧你的小老鼠爪子\N{\fs38}And why aren't you clenching your little rat hands in anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想让我失败\N{\fs38}You didn't want me to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我成功\N{\fs38}You wanted me to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs38}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在找借口把你升到一个文职上去\N{\fs38}I was looking for an excuse to promote you to a desk job,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就把这个借口放在银盘子上\N{\fs38}and you handed it to me on a silver platter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的小老鼠爪子奉上了\N{\fs38}with your little rat hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不\N{\fs38}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对九九片区说再见吧 Raymond\N{\fs38}Say good-bye to the Nine-Nine, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要任命你为纽约警局的公共关系部长\N{\fs38}I'm making you head of NYPD Public Relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警监 过来和我一起\N{\fs38}Captain, get in here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 对镜头微笑 Raymond\N{\fs38}Go ahead. Smile for the cameras, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的新工作了\N{\fs38}That's your new job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs38}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点 我们来背对背摆造型\N{\fs38}Okay, quick, let's pose back-to-back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双手交叉再来个神气的斜笑\N{\fs38}with our arms crossed and a cocky smirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做吗 双手交叉了没\N{\fs38}You doing it? Your arms crossed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 手放下 那也不错\N{\fs38}No, arms down. That's good.
